    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Trend Phrase Detector\\n\",\"**NLP Project 77 of 100** — Surface emerging phrases and slang from text data over time.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Synthetic social posts with temporal signal\\nbase = ['machine learning','deep learning','AI','neural network'] * 30\\nemerging = ['vibe coding','agentic AI','MCP protocol','reasoning model','thinking tokens'] * 20\\n\\nposts = []\\nfor t in base:\\n    date = pd.Timestamp('2025-01-01') + pd.Timedelta(days=int(rng.integers(0,180)))\\n    posts.append({'text': f'Working on {t} today', 'date': date})\\nfor t in emerging:\\n    date = pd.Timestamp('2025-04-01') + pd.Timedelta(days=int(rng.integers(0,90)))  # Recent\\n    posts.append({'text': f'Everyone is talking about {t}', 'date': date})\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(posts).sort_values('date').reset_index(drop=True)\\ndf['month'] = df['date'].dt.to_period('M').astype(str)\\nprint(f'Posts: {len(df)}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import CountVectorizer\\n\\n# Compare early vs recent phrase frequencies\\nearly = df[df['date'] < '2025-04-01']['text']\\nrecent = df[df['date'] >= '2025-04-01']['text']\\n\\ncv = CountVectorizer(ngram_range=(1,2), max_features=100)\\ncv.fit(pd.concat([early, recent]))\\n\\nearly_freq = cv.transform(early).sum(axis=0).A1\\nrecent_freq = cv.transform(recent).sum(axis=0).A1\\n\\nterms = cv.get_feature_names_out()\\n# Trending = high recent freq, low early freq\\ntrending_score = (recent_freq + 1) / (early_freq + 1)\\ntop_trending = trending_score.argsort()[-10:][::-1]\\n\\nprint('🔥 Trending Phrases (recent vs early):')\\nfor i in top_trending:\\n    print(f'  {terms[i]:25s} | Early: {int(early_freq[i]):3d} → Recent: {int(recent_freq[i]):3d} | Score: {trending_score[i]:.1f}x')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Trend detection compares phrase frequency** across time periods.\\n\",\"- **Rising terms indicate emerging topics** worth monitoring.\\n\",\"- **For production, use sliding windows** and alert on spikes.\\n\",\"- **Combine with sentiment** to detect positive vs negative trends.\"]}\n",
